.1335, 43.0701, 44.074, 46.564, 46.973, 47.2942, 47.5908, 48.3575, 48.5393, 49.6077, 47.7591, 48.3105, 52.3366, 51.7654, 52.6048, 52.3929, 51.4049, 51.7499, 50.9077, 52.5463, 51.3401, 51.2595, 52.9484, 52.0159, 51.4499, 51.0797, 51.2325, 50.3394, 50.0628, 51.3743, 50.2776, 49.9671, 49.8705, 49.7328, 49.3981, 49.6087, 48.4445, 42.2675, 42.0296, 39.6742, 39.7329, 41.7495, 40.5083, 40.1409, 40.1061, 39.7964, 39.6244, 39.8989, 38.6708, 38.8391, 38.8308, 37.6665, 37.0395, 38.6379, 38.0886, 38.5664, 38.0446, 38.3933, 39.0883, 39.3123, 37.5224, 36.8609, 37.0547, 38.4122, 37.8701, 39.1551, 38.7522, 38.9589, 39.7639, 38.3296, 37.7515, 36.1622, 34.6877, 35.3324, 35.0344, 33.4664, 34.6416, 34.4884, 35.9115, 36.3809, 36.6081, 37.2898, 36.6646, 34.8815, 35.7745, 35.1328, 35.1015, 35.1441, 35.4368, 34.0618, 35.9298, 35.8151, 35.5782, 36.3868, 36.1219, 34.9744, 36.6055, 36.6404, 37.0365, 36.8261, 36.3941, 37.5866, 38.8885, 38.2118, 38.6428, 38.9102, 38.1745, 39.4947, 39.7126, 41.9758, 45.2263, 45.4376, 45.9231, 46.152, 45.142, 46.8438, 46.5403, 46.5326, 47.2757, 46.0045, 45.2886, 45.7864, 45.5744, 45.016, 43.9577, 45.5646, 47.2529, 45.5103, 44.7899, 44.4989, 43.9951, 44.4973, 44.8434, 45.6689, 45.5974, 45.7972, 46.3203, 45.9007, 46.1761, 47.4322, 46.266, 45.605, 45.647, 47.4748, 45.7949, 44.466, 44.6129, 45.0194, 45.1116, 45.9068, 45.824, 45.7307, 45.7064, 46.8554, 45.879, 43.3579, 44.0865, 44.7963, 43.1781, 41.3607, 41.4244, 41.3267, 42.4008, 42.7231, 43.0871, 41.4231, 41.2026, 40.4194, 40.9116, 40.9644, 42.133, 40.3907, 39.1108, 39.6607, 41.919, 40.1287, 41.5704, 40.8202, 40.2407, 42.7245, 41.4891, 42.5157, 42.6551, 41.8572, 41.3538, 41.4554, 42.3553, 42.2902, 42.0289, 40.6984, 40.2867, 40.2057, 39.9573, 40.007, 39.4906, 39.0692, 37.4137, 38.4418, 39.7388, 40.2713, 40.1703, 38.7159, 38.702, 39.1107, 38.857, 39.5203, 40.8981, 38.5036, 38.0509, 36.9329, 35.5341, 33.9305, 35.6781, 37.9321, 37.0043, 37.5426, 37.2624, 37.4272, 39.0028, 39.8033, 40.4758, 41.646, 41.895, 42.1026, 43.1615, 42.7207, 42.5532, 43.1551, 41.8062, 41.822, 41.4497, 41.1766, 40.1353, 39.3796, 40.0135, 39.0454, 37.4787, 36.5781, 36.8095, 37.3183, 38.3506, 42.0833, 40.24, 38.3543, 41.1116, 41.9277, 41.1625, 41.7026, 40.369, 41.1045, 39.6252, 40.1916, 38.9923, 40.4064, 38.645, 36.3502, 32.9915, 33.3219, 31.31, 29.4015, 29.853, 32.3155, 29.3804, 28.0857, 28.7886, 26.5112, 27.6386, 23.1584, 19.4028, 22.066, 24.5581, 22.2931, null, null], "summary_html": "<h1>反转因子的精细结构 -- 理想反转因子 M</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>本策略将东吴证券提出的\"W式切割\"反转因子方法应用于商品期货。核心思路是：传统反转因子（如过去N日收益率）可以按日内交易活跃度进行\"切割\"——大单交易活跃日的涨跌幅具有更强的反转特性（信息驱动），而小单交易日的涨跌幅更接近噪声甚至呈现弱动量。通过分离这两部分并做差，得到\"理想反转因子\"M，其选股/选品种能力显著优于传统反转因子。</p>\n<p>在商品期货中，我们使用日频 amount/volume（平均成交金额/手数）作为\"平均单笔成交金额\"的代理指标。对每个品种回看过去N个交易日，按该指标排序分为高D组（大单日）和低D组（小单日），分别计算累积收益，M = M_high - M_low。高M品种（大单日涨幅大于小单日）倾向于反转——做空；低M品种倾向于继续——做多。等权组合N=20和N=40两个窗口，进一步降低参数敏感性。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>0.05</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>0.2%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>4.1%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-16.9%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.08</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3430</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>0.54</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>-0.69</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>0.61 / 0.48</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2012</th><th>2013</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-2.02</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-1.71</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-1.96</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.51</span></td><td>0.82</td><td>0.61</td><td>0.39</td><td>0.32</td><td>1.22</td><td>1.06</td><td>0.63</td><td>0.54</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.14</span></td><td>0.03</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-3.51</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>open</code></td><td>开盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>high</code></td><td>最高价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>low</code></td><td>最低价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>volume</code></td><td>成交量</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>amount</code></td><td>成交额</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每日</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3432</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>98.7%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>39.3</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p>对品种 <span class=\"math-tex\">s</span>，回溯 <span class=\"math-tex\">N</span> 个交易日，计算每日平均成交金额：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">D_t = \\frac{\\text{amount}_t}{\\text{volume}_t}</div>\n<p>将 <span class=\"math-tex\">N</span> 日按 <span class=\"math-tex\">D</span> 从大到小排序，取前 <span class=\"math-tex\">N/2</span> 为高D组，后 <span class=\"math-tex\">N/2</span> 为低D组：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">M_{\\text{high}} = \\prod_{t \\in \\text{highD}} (1 + R_t) - 1</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">M_{\\text{low}} = \\prod_{t \\in \\text{lowD}} (1 + R_t) - 1</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">M = M_{\\text{high}} - M_{\\text{low}}</div>\n<p>截面排名后转连续信号 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\in [-1, 1]</span>，乘以波动率目标缩放系数得到仓位。</p>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<p><strong>R1 (Sharpe 0.74)</strong>: 初始实现了完整的W式切割逻辑，覆盖N=20/40/60三种窗口，每种搭配hold=5/10/20三种再平衡周期，加上M_high和M_low独立因子变体共12个。诊断发现N=20、hold=20是最优组合，短hold（5天）的变体Sharpe为负，说明信号衰减缓慢，频繁调仓反而增加了交易成本（换手率1.06）。截面IC仅0.006，时序IC=0.007（65%品种IC&gt;0），信号在部分品种有效。</p>\n<p><strong>R2 (Sharpe 0.84)</strong>: 根据R1诊断，延长再平衡周期至hold=25并加入IC gate过滤弱品种。结果hold=25（M_N20_h25_raw Sharpe 0.84）确实优于hold=20（0.74），验证了信号慢衰减的判断。IC gate版本与非gate版本几乎相同（被dedup），说明品种过滤对该因子帮助有限。换手率降至0.85。</p>\n<p><strong>R3 (Sharpe 1.00)</strong>: <strong>关键转折</strong>: 引入N=20与N=40的等权组合（M_combo_N20_N40），利用不同窗口的互补性降低波动（年化vol从66.5%降至46.8%），Sharpe从0.84提升至1.00。同时测试了更长hold（30, 40天）和VWAP替代指标，发现hold&gt;25开始退化（hold=30仅0.03），VWAP/close替代效果差（均为负），说明amount/volume是更好的大单活跃度指标。半样本Sharpe前1.31后1.09，策略在样本前后均稳健。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频（daily），使用 amount 和 volume 计算平均成交金额</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全品种商品期货（58个品种）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 约25个交易日再平衡，属于中低频策略</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - 原文使用A股逐笔\"成交笔数\"数据，期货端用 amount/volume 近似，可能有信息损失\n<p>- 截面IC较弱（0.010），主要靠时序IC（0.009）驱动收益 - 年度Sharpe波动较大（2019年-0.03，2022年-0.02），部分年份接近持平 - 最大回撤58%较高，建议结合其他因子分散风险</p>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>N_WINDOWS</code></td><td><code>[20, 40]</code></td><td>lookback windows for M factor</td></tr><tr><td><code>HOLD_DAYS</code></td><td><code>25</code></td><td>rebalance hold period</td></tr><tr><td><code>SPLIT_RATIO</code></td><td><code>0.5</code></td><td>top/bottom half split</td></tr><tr><td><code>MIN_VALID_RATIO</code></td><td><code>0.6</code></td><td>minimum valid data ratio in window</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 0.991</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 13.93s</li>\n</ul>"}